metadata.description: Crazy camel is now in the world of metaverse!  Mad camel is walking in the desert unaware of everything. The sun is directly overhead and thirst has exhausted him. Suddenly, a cactus appears in front of him and begins to eat it to quench his thirst. He doesn't know that this cactus is one of the most poisonous plants in that area. After eating the cactus, he gets sleepy and lies next to a bush. Now the environment feels different to him. He starts to feel dizzy and as soon as he opens and closes his eyes, he sees an amusement park in front of him. She runs to the amusement park even though it's too good to be true. He gets on the first bullet train he sees and has fun like kids. While getting on most of the machines in the amusement park, he suddenly realizes that he has run out of money and sits on the bank.  Join us if you want the crazy camel to have more fun at the amusement park…  10000 Nft is waiting for you with its collection...
